reviews.reviewerName: Valerie at Abundant Life Nutritional Therapy
reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and sturdy - well worth the price!
reviews.reviewText: This was easy for me to assemble by myself (no hubby needed lol) and the materials feel heavy-duty and quite sturdy. I used this to display products for sale in my nutritional business and it works GREAT for that and its modern look updates the space well. A great bargain for $60 - get it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just as described
reviews.reviewText: Pretty good quality, decent space, simple sleek appearance, really easy to assemble, decent value for product

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Exactly as advertised. Sturdy, spacious and was easy to put together

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks good and easy to put together
reviews.reviewText: Took 2 people about 20 minutes of work, but could be done by one. It comes with adjustable feet so using those makes it perfectly sturdy. One all screws are fully tightened it’s not wobbly. Nice height too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It was easy to put together and pretty solid once you did so. It’s a very attractive shelf. Happy about it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a pretty good buy if you’re looking for something stylish and easy to put up. The only problem I ran into was that the screws you put at the bottom of the shelf to keep it leveled were different sizes, so I could not use them. I was still able to use the shelf, but I would’ve liked to use all of the parts to the shelf. Besides that, I love this shelf.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 4 tier ladder shelf
reviews.reviewText: Very easy to put together and sturdy. I really like the black frame with the wood shelf. it’s exactly what I was looking for.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I needed a 4 tier not too big or too small Ladder bookshelf for the holidays. This was the perfect size for Items we wanted to display for the Holiday's. Very pleased. Packaging good, delivery on time and very easy to put together.
I love it. It works great in the kitchen. Holds alot of things.
This is a great shelving unit. Solid enough and hold a lot - looks great in my living room!
